    "content": {
        "title": "Configuring the UI from Action Editor",
        "body": "<ol>\n<li>From the left menu of the <strong>Action Editor</strong>, under the <strong>Widget</strong> section, select <strong>Set Widget Property</strong>.</li>\n<li>From the right pane, under <strong>Mobile Forms</strong> &gt; <strong>frmAddRecipients</strong> > <b>flexAddRecipient</b> > <strong> flexFieldsContainer</strong> &gt; <strong>flexAdd</strong> &gt; <strong>flexBorderedButton</strong>, and then select <strong>btnSquared</strong>.</li>\n<li>In the right pane, modify the following values:\n<ul>\n<li>Property: <strong>Opacity</strong></li>\n<li>Value: <strong>100 %</strong></li>\n</ul>\n</li>\n</ol>"
    },
